You look miserable.

19
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:27,750
Yeah, It hurts a lot.

20
00:02:30,541 --> 00:02:32,541
Fortunately...

21
00:02:32,625 --> 00:02:35,458
...I think I at least know
what's causing the ulcer.

22
00:02:35,541 --> 00:02:36,875
[SAYA]
It's sorta obvious.

23
00:02:36,958 --> 00:02:38,541
I blame myself!

24
00:02:38,625 --> 00:02:40,958
I've been staying up late
thinking about <i>dagashi,</i>

25
00:02:41,041 --> 00:02:42,500
and now I have this ulcer!

26
00:02:42,583 --> 00:02:43,500
[SAYA]
That's not why.

27
00:02:43,583 --> 00:02:44,750
[HOTARU]
Uh?

28
00:02:44,833 --> 00:02:46,208
Then what's causing it?

29
00:02:46,291 --> 00:02:47,750
[gasps]

30
00:02:47,833 --> 00:02:50,583
Maybe it's the stress of
not being able to eat <i>dagashi</i>

31
00:02:50,666 --> 00:02:52,458
more than three times a day?

32
00:02:53,625 --> 00:02:55,625
Well, um, I'm not a
doctor or anything,

33
00:02:55,708 --> 00:02:57,791
but I really don't think
either of those reasons

34
00:02:57,875 --> 00:02:59,541
could cause you to
get a mouth ulcer.

35
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:02,708
But there is a more
obvious explanation.

36
00:03:02,791 --> 00:03:04,916
Super obvious.

37
00:03:07,541 --> 00:03:11,083
Wait. Are you saying it's
because I eat too much <i>dagashi?</i>

38
00:03:11,166 --> 00:03:12,875
