39
00:03:12,958 --> 00:03:13,750
That's a bingo!

40
00:03:13,833 --> 00:03:16,041
No way! I reckon that's wrong!

41
00:03:16,125 --> 00:03:18,916
[SAYA] What? Are you
serious right now, Hotaru?

42
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:23,166
Another thing, what did I
just hear? An accent? Huh?

43
00:03:24,416 --> 00:03:26,458
[HOTARU giggles]

44
00:03:26,541 --> 00:03:27,416
[gasps]

45
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:29,208
No, don't eat that!

46
00:03:29,291 --> 00:03:31,416
This is the absolute
worst thing you could eat

47
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,333
with a mouth ulcer!

48
00:03:33,416 --> 00:03:34,875
Candy's not my thing,

49
00:03:34,958 --> 00:03:37,833
but even I know this stuff
crackles and pops in your mouth.

50
00:03:37,916 --> 00:03:39,625
You're right on target, Master!

51
00:03:39,708 --> 00:03:43,125
As you may already know,
this snack is called <i>watapachi.</i>

52
00:03:43,208 --> 00:03:45,458
This sneaky snack
disguises itself

53
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:47,958
as a sweet, innocent,
cotton candy puffball.

54
00:03:48,041 --> 00:03:50,208
In reality though,
it's actually harboring

55
00:03:50,291 --> 00:03:53,125
tiny ninja-like crackles
that pop in your mouth.

56
00:03:53,208 --> 00:03:54,541
Talk about a shock!

57
00:03:56,666 --> 00:03:58,125
Exactly!

58
00:03:58,208 --> 00:03:59,583
So if you eat <i>watapachi</i>
while you have a mouth ulcer,

59
00:03:59,666 --> 00:04:02,000
it's gonna hurt like hell!
It's a bad idea!

60
00:04:02,083 --> 00:04:05,500
Probably. Even still, I want it.

61
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:09,500
[HOTARU]
The fact that I shouldn't eat it

62
00:04:09,583 --> 00:04:11,625
is what makes this
snack so irresistible.

63
00:04:11,708 --> 00:04:13,458
Like a forbidden fruit!

64
00:04:13,541 --> 00:04:14,875
[SAYA yelping]

65
00:04:14,958 --> 00:04:16,916
