66
00:04:19,791 --> 00:04:21,583
Hotaru, no!

67
00:04:22,708 --> 00:04:24,708
Oh yeah! Now that's
what I'm talking about!

68
00:04:24,791 --> 00:04:27,500
It hurts me so good!

69
00:04:27,583 --> 00:04:28,958
[SAYA sighs]

70
00:04:35,708 --> 00:04:39,000
No, don't!

71
00:04:39,083 --> 00:04:41,541
Isn't the stuff at the
bottom like super sour?

72
00:04:41,625 --> 00:04:42,833
Indeed!

73
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:44,833
In the bottom of
every <i>watapachi</i> bag,

74
00:04:44,916 --> 00:04:46,000
