75
00:04:46,083 --> 00:04:48,666
that fell off the
cotton candy part!

76
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:52,833
These guys pack a punch so bad,
it'll make your tears cry tears!

77
00:04:52,916 --> 00:04:54,291
[SAYA]
Sounds kinda painful.

78
00:04:54,375 --> 00:04:56,291
Probably excruciating!

79
00:04:56,375 --> 00:04:57,708
[SAYA gasps]

80
00:04:57,791 --> 00:04:59,208
[SAYA]
Stop!

81
00:04:59,291 --> 00:05:00,916
You're crazy.

82
00:05:09,125 --> 00:05:10,750
Where am I?

83
00:05:10,833 --> 00:05:11,583
[gasps]

84
00:05:11,666 --> 00:05:12,875
