85
00:05:12,958 --> 00:05:15,708
Hey there, buddy. Come on,
you need to get up!

86
00:05:15,791 --> 00:05:17,625
Looks like the time has
come for us to crackle.

87
00:05:17,708 --> 00:05:19,416
Let's make some tears cry tears!

