00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,875
But we just got here.

89
00:05:20,958 --> 00:05:22,125
Yeah, I know.

90
00:05:22,208 --> 00:05:23,875
I was kinda hoping we'd
have more time together.

91
00:05:23,958 --> 00:05:27,083
Hey, we'll always have
the <i>watapachi</i> bag, right?

92
00:05:27,166 --> 00:05:28,666
[gasps]

93
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:30,208
Whoa. Is something wrong?

94
00:05:30,291 --> 00:05:33,250
Listen kid, my time here
is up. Don't cry for me.

95
00:05:33,333 --> 00:05:36,500
What? No! Wait!

96
00:05:36,583 --> 00:05:38,666
Don't leave me here all alone!

97
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:43,625
I'm glad we met. I promise
I'll find you on the other side!

98
00:05:43,708 --> 00:05:46,541
No, please! Don't leave me!

99
00:05:46,625 --> 00:05:48,833
See ya later, my comrade!

100
00:05:48,916 --> 00:05:51,833
Please don't go!

101
00:05:51,916 --> 00:05:56,250
[screaming]

102
00:05:56,333 --> 00:05:59,125
[HOTARU crying]

103
00:05:59,208 --> 00:06:00,500
What's going on?

104
00:06:00,583 --> 00:06:01,583
Are you crying in pain

105
00:06:01,666 --> 00:06:04,291
or because of something
weird again?

106
00:06:04,375 --> 00:06:05,625
[SAYA sighs]

107
00:06:05,708 --> 00:06:08,625
So, is your ulcer
still bothering you?

108
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:10,041
What ulcer?

109
00:06:10,125 --> 00:06:12,125
[SAYA] The one in your mouth!
Is there more than one?

110
00:06:12,208 --> 00:06:14,125
It's crackle time! Ta-ta!

111
00:06:14,208 --> 00:06:15,375
[screaming]

112
00:06:15,458 --> 00:06:17,625
A piece of the <i>watapachi</i>
ended up popping

113
00:06:17,708 --> 00:06:19,250
