115
00:06:20,916 --> 00:06:24,625
No! Hearing you in pain makes
me feel like I'm in pain, too!

116
00:06:24,708 --> 00:06:27,166
My tears are crying
tears it hurts so bad!

117
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:28,541
I can't take it!

118
00:06:28,625 --> 00:06:30,416
This unbearably
painful crackling

119
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:33,708
can only be described
in one way!

120
00:06:33,791 --> 00:06:37,916
It's like walking down a
path of untainted bliss!

121
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,083
Seriously? You really
are one kinky chick.

122
00:06:41,166 --> 00:06:42,625
[HOTARU]
And so...

123
00:06:45,041 --> 00:06:48,541
Hey, I just noticed that
Kokonotsu is missing in action.

124
00:06:48,625 --> 00:06:50,708
You're a little late
to the obvious party.

125
00:06:50,791 --> 00:06:52,000
I don't know where he's at.

126
00:06:52,083 --> 00:06:54,208
He was already gone
when I got here.

127
00:06:54,291 --> 00:06:55,250
