128
00:07:00,083 --> 00:07:01,541
[gasps]

129
00:07:01,625 --> 00:07:03,458
[SAYA]
Oh my gosh, these are too cute!

130
00:07:03,541 --> 00:07:05,125
They're crazy adorable, right?

131
00:07:05,208 --> 00:07:07,041
