notice them, Master.

132
00:07:07,125 --> 00:07:09,291
Well, I'm not be a big
fan of candy like you,

133
00:07:09,375 --> 00:07:12,041
but I'm a total sucker when
it comes to anything cute.

134
00:07:12,125 --> 00:07:13,625
[HOTARU]
A lot of <i>dagashi</i> manufacturers

135
00:07:13,708 --> 00:07:15,666
are trying out new ways
to improve their appeal

136
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:18,250
and expand their reach
within potential markets.

137
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:20,750
