popular right now.

138
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:23,291
Oh, makes sense, I guess.

139
00:07:23,375 --> 00:07:26,541
It's my pleasure to
present: Lucky Poo!

140
00:07:27,791 --> 00:07:31,125
