144
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:40,375
[SAYA]
No way.

145
00:07:40,458 --> 00:07:42,750
Surely she doesn't
really mean poo.

146
00:07:42,833 --> 00:07:45,500
Well, in any case, they're
beyond cute, no doubt!

147
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:48,500
I agree! And as a bonus!
