154
00:08:00,083 --> 00:08:02,500
then the candy pops
out of this rear hole!

155
00:08:02,583 --> 00:08:04,541
Seriously?! Ew!

156
00:08:04,625 --> 00:08:07,791
Seriously! Little kids eat
this stuff up, literally!

157
00:08:07,875 --> 00:08:10,208
[SAYA]
