when it comes to
<i>dagashi,</i> but um...

165
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,833
...perhaps you should try
to be a little more mature

166
00:08:26,916 --> 00:08:29,708
and, you know, lead by example.

167
00:08:29,791 --> 00:08:32,958
I understand,
and I agree 100%.

168
00:08:33,041 --> 00:08:35,375
Uh. Awesome! So you
get what I'm saying?

169
00:08:35,458 --> 00:08:36,125
[HOTARU]
Yes.

170
00:08:36,208 --> 00:08:38,041
That's such a relief.

171
00:08:38,125 --> 00:08:40,666
