<i>dagashi</i> tea party!

175
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,500
[giggles]

176
00:08:49,958 --> 00:08:52,416
[HOTARU] It is a rather
pleasant and sunny afternoon.

177
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:55,750
My good friend and I are
spending the day together.

178
00:08:55,833 --> 00:08:58,333
These moments never
feel long enough.

179
00:08:58,416 --> 00:09:00,000
While we often have
different preferences

180
