the same snack.

183
00:09:06,416 --> 00:09:08,583
We might not always
agree with each other,

184
00:09:08,666 --> 00:09:11,750
but when it comes to delicacies,
we're of the same mind.

185
00:09:11,833 --> 00:09:14,583
