199
00:09:41,041 --> 00:09:42,541
Hotaru, you may
not realize this,

200
00:09:42,625 --> 00:09:44,125
but a poo party
sounds really gross.

201
00:09:44,208 --> 00:09:46,208
It does? I wonder why?

202
00:09:47,458 --> 00:09:48,958
[SAYA] The way the candy
comes out of the end

203
00:09:49,041 --> 00:09:51,458
makes it even more disgusting.

204
00:09:51,541 --> 00:09:53,666
[HOTARU] Here, Master.
Hold out your hand.

205
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:55,333
[whimpers]

206
00:09:57,958 --> 00:09:59,750
