239
00:11:22,625 --> 00:11:24,833
But it's called Lucky Poo!

240
00:11:28,208 --> 00:11:29,666
[KOKONOTSU]
Hey, I'm back.

241
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:30,875
Oh.

242
00:11:30,958 --> 00:11:33,375
Hotaru! I didn't
know you were here.

243
00:11:34,416 --> 00:11:37,291
Heya, Kokonotsu!
I'm glad you're back!

244
00:11:37,375 --> 00:11:38,916
You were gone a while.

245
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,208
Oh yeah, you just
missed Master Saya.

246
00:11:41,291 --> 00:11:43,375
She didn't tell me
she was coming by.

247
00:11:43,458 --> 00:11:44,416
Uh?

248
00:11:46,875 --> 00:11:48,333
[KOKONOTSU]
