499
00:23:57,916 --> 00:23:59,916
but why would you
think Sakura Daikon is?

500
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:00,958
[chuckles]

501
00:24:01,041 --> 00:24:02,583
[HOTARU]
Excellent question, Master!

502
00:24:02,666 --> 00:24:04,875
Sakura Daikon is made
with sweetened vinegar.

503
00:24:04,958 --> 00:24:06,916
And vinegar and salt have
something in common!

504
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:07,791
[gasps]

505
00:24:07,875 --> 00:24:09,291
[SAYA]
Wait.

506
00:24:09,375 --> 00:24:11,166
[HOTARU] Both of them sting
like crazy on an open wound!

507
00:24:11,250 --> 00:24:12,333
[screams]

508
00:24:12,416 --> 00:24:13,708
[HOTARU] Just wait
until the next episode.

509
00:24:13,791 --> 00:24:15,250
It's "that kind of story!"

510
00:24:15,333 --> 00:24:17,458
[SAYA] What? I don't even
know what that means!

511
00:24:17,541 --> 00:24:19,958
[HOTARU]
Until next time, snack warriors!

